"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/997724","Department for Education","false","2018-11-07","<p>There are currently 176 members of staff on an apprenticeship programme within the department.</p><p>Recently published data detailing the Civil Service performance against the first year of the public sector apprenticeship target can be found here:</p><p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/civil-service-apprenticeship-data-2017-to-2018" target="_blank">https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/civil-service-apprenticeship-data-2017-to-2018</a>.</p>","Guildford","Anne Milton",,"2018-11-07T13:14:36.537Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/997724/answer","Biography information for Anne Milton","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/997724/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/997724/answer",,,,,"60","Education","Education","2018-10-30","Department for Education: Apprentices","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Education, how many apprentices are employed in his Department.","false","Biography information for David Linden","Glasgow East","David Linden","185747"
