"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/997727","Cabinet Office","false","2018-11-06","<p>The Cabinet Office currently employs 72 apprentices who are actively completing an apprenticeship, this equates to 1.12% of our workforce.</p>","Hertsmere","Oliver Dowden",,"2018-11-06T15:02:21.557Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/997727/answer","Biography information for Oliver Dowden","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/997727/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/997727/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2018-10-30","Cabinet Office: Apprentices","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, how many apprentices are employed in his Department.","false","Biography information for David Linden","Glasgow East","David Linden","185750"
